entries.femaleVariant: Choom, I'm tellin' ya. One puff and you're a fuckin' blur out there.
Best thing is, come down happens way later. Just enough time to wrap up the gig and hit the sack.
Somethin' new like that hits the market, mercs suddenly start dyin' off like flies.
One guy's heart stops tickin', another one's coprocessor overheats...
Nah, all rumors. Just 'cause some gonks OD doesn't mean I gotta quit. Everything in moderation.
Chem's part of the job, just like chrome. You don't use it, you don't get results. Simple as that.
